sources.title: Western, Romance | My Outlaw Brother | Mickey Rooney, Robert Preston & Don 'Red' Barry
sources.description:
He followed a dangerous trail... to a beautiful woman and the deadliest killer! A young man travels to Mexico in search of his brother, who has become involved with a dangerous gang.

Director: Elliott Nugent
Writers: Gene Fowler Jr. , Alfred Lewis Levitt 
Stars: Mickey Rooney, Wanda Hendrix, Robert Preston & Don 'Red' Barry
Genres: Classics, Action, Romance, Western
